bug.author: AlexDBlack
bug.summary: ND4J: TensorFlowConversion doesn't support many ND4J datatypes
bug.description:
Essentially it hasn't kept up with our new datatype additions: <denchmark-link:https://github.com/eclipse/deeplearning4j/blob/master/nd4j/nd4j-tensorflow/src/main/java/org/nd4j/tensorflow/conversion/TensorflowConversion.java#L109-L129>https://github.com/eclipse/deeplearning4j/blob/master/nd4j/nd4j-tensorflow/src/main/java/org/nd4j/tensorflow/conversion/TensorflowConversion.java#L109-L129</denchmark-link>
For example missing unsigned, bfloat16, etc. We should also test these.
